Since 2019 ADHO SIG liaison & SIG representative on ADHO COB (Constituent Organizing Board).

Since 2017 Founding member and current chair of international Special Interest Group Digital Literary Stylistics (SIG-DLS) of the Alliance of Digital Humanities Organizations (ADHO).

Session chair at various international conferences within Digital Humanities, Empirical Studies of Literature, Metaphor Studies, Cognitive Literary Studies, and Stylistics.

2012-2016 Founding member and organizer Postdoc-Plattform Gttinger Philologisches Forum (GpF) (with Kai Sina and Peer Trilcke).
